  "env_id": "odoo_inventory_env@0.1",
  "description": "We are migrating our consumer electronics catalog to Odoo. Log in as admin/admin and import the 12 products from /home/ga/Desktop/product_catalog.csv. Map the legacy CSV headers to Odoo fields as follows: 'Product Name' to 'Name', 'SKU' to 'Internal Reference', 'Category' to 'Product Category', 'Unit Cost' to 'Cost', 'Retail Price' to 'Sales Price', 'Type' to 'Product Type', and 'Weight (kg)' to 'Weight'. Ensure all 12 products are successfully imported with their attributes correctly mapped.",
